  "detailed_description": "Explore a world of intrigue and mystery.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nParadox of the Cryptomancers features mind-bending puzzles similar to those in Myst.<br />\r\nAnd, like Ready Player One, this is a treasure hunt of epic proportions.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMysteries are scattered throughout many dimensions, each with a cryptic secret to be discovered.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDuring launch, a new puzzle will be unlocked each day for all to join the fray.  Race to solve each puzzle first.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThere will be 20 challenging puzzles to be tackled.  Be prepared: some are not for the faint of heart.  They may require deep scrutiny and clever solutions.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGet ready.",
  "about_the_game": "Explore a world of intrigue and mystery.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nParadox of the Cryptomancers features mind-bending puzzles similar to those in Myst.<br />\r\nAnd, like Ready Player One, this is a treasure hunt of epic proportions.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMysteries are scattered throughout many dimensions, each with a cryptic secret to be discovered.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDuring launch, a new puzzle will be unlocked each day for all to join the fray.  Race to solve each puzzle first.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThere will be 20 challenging puzzles to be tackled.  Be prepared: some are not for the faint of heart.  They may require deep scrutiny and clever solutions.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGet ready.",
